Woman's Day - January 2014  USA

110 Pages | True PDF | English | 28 MB 


Woman's Day Magazine covers many topics of interest to women, making it one of the leading magazines in the country. Each issue features a variety of articles relating to home improvement, cooking, fashion, and family. Designed for women on a budget, many of the issues come with tips on saving money on clothing, food, and travel.
